data.chText: （犯罪组织，尤指黑手党的）头面人物，首领
data.enText: a very powerful man in a criminal organization, especially the Mafia
a person who began or developed sth

data.chText: 他是鬅客摇滚乐的创始人。

means: (犯罪组织，尤指黑手党的)头面人物，首领

tr: someone having a relation analogous to that of a male sponsor to his godchild
any man who serves as a sponsor for a child at baptism

value.def: A powerful man who is at the head of a criminal organization is sometimes referred to as a godfather .

example.tran: 令人畏惧的黑手党头目

value.tran: 犯罪集团的头目；黑帮老大

value.def: You can refer to a man who started or developed something such as a style of music as the godfather of that thing.

example.tran: 灵乐的开创者詹姆斯· 布朗
